com.strongloop.android.remoting
Class VirtualObject

java.lang.Object
  com.strongloop.android.remoting.VirtualObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Model
public class VirtualObject
extends java.lang.Object

A local representative of a single virtual object. The behavior of this object is defined through a prototype defined on the server, and the identity of this instance is defined through its `creationParameters`.
